# The `SmallVectorImpl` Class Template Reference

<DoxygenPage pluginConfig={pluginConfig}>

This class consists of common code factored out of the <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/smallvector">SmallVector</a> class to reduce code duplication based on the <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/smallvector">SmallVector</a> &#39;N&#39; template parameter. <a href="#details">More...</a>

## Declaration

class llvm::SmallVectorImpl&lt;T&gt;</CodeBlock>

## Description {#details}

This class consists of common code factored out of the <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/smallvector">SmallVector</a> class to reduce code duplication based on the <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/smallvector">SmallVector</a> &#39;N&#39; template parameter.
